This product includes software derived from n8n.

The following functions in nodes/AgentLangfuse/execute.ts are derived from
`ToolsAgent/common.ts` in the package @n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain, published by
n8n GmbH under the Sustainable Use License:

  fixEmptyContentMessage
  getAgentStepsParser
  handleAgentFinishOutput
  handleParsedStepOutput
  extractBinaryMessages
  getOutputParserSchema

They were copied from an earlier revision of that file and three of them have
since drifted from it. Compared with n8n's current agent, this node does not pass
PDF or text attachments through to the model, does not filter thinking content
blocks out of a final answer, and re-wraps an output parser result that is
already shaped as {output: ...}. Closing that gap is tracked separately.

